bels' Orchesterwerk »Surrogate Cities«. Neben ausführlichen Darstellungen der Projekte bietet diese Studie exklusive Interviews, u.a. mit Klaus Meine (»Scorpions«), Joey DeMaio (»Manowar«) und Peter Brem (Berliner Philharmoniker).  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aKlassische MusikxRezeptionxRockmusik. 0aMusikxRockmusik. 0aRockmusikxMusik. 4aFilmmusik. 4aHeavy Metal. 4aManowar. 4aMetallica. 4aMusik. 4aMusikwissenschaft. 4aPopkultur. 4aPopmusik. 4aRockmusik. 4aScorpions. 4aSting. 7aMUSIC / History & Criticism.2bisacsh  aMusicology.  aPop Music.  aPopular Culture.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2000-2009z9783110463415oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2000-2009z978311046340840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839412497zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839412497423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839412497/original  a978-3-11-046340-8  transcript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2000-2009c2000d2009  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2000d2009